        {"speaker": "clerk", "spanish": "¿Qué talla necesita?", "english": "What size do you need?"},
        {"speaker": "customer", "spanish": "Mediana, por favor.", "english": "Medium, please."},
        {"speaker": "clerk", "spanish": "¿Le gusta este color?", "english": "Do you like this color?"},
        {"speaker": "customer", "spanish": "Sí, me gusta. ¿Cuánto cuesta?", "english": "Yes, I like it. How much does it cost?"},
        {"speaker": "clerk", "spanish": "Veinte euros.", "english": "Twenty euros."},
        {"speaker": "customer", "spanish": "Perfecto. La llevo.", "english": "Perfect. I'll take it."},
        {"speaker": "clerk", "spanish": "¿Paga con tarjeta o efectivo?", "english": "Are you paying by card or cash?"},
        {"speaker": "customer", "spanish": "Con tarjeta, por favor.", "english": "By card, please."}
      ],
      "vocabulary": ["camiseta", "talla", "mediana", "color", "euros", "tarjeta", "efectivo"],
      "tips": "Tallas: pequeña (small), mediana (medium), grande (large). Know basic colors and numbers."
